{"tid":1614411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［公關］維持正當性嘅最好方法就係唔好打錯無辜","createTime":"2019-10-02T18:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T04:45:31.000Z","uid":157064,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a39845a2a708815644c28533fe621449752397d0","tid":1614411,"uid":157064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:49:33.000Z","msg":"只係提返大家啊媽係女人嘅道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n運動到呢個階段其實黃藍比例真係固定咗<br />\n嗰啲所謂中立理性嘅人只會坐係屋企睇電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而公關除咗係畀屋企嘅朋友睇之外，最重要當然就畀外國傳媒睇。好多時我地做嘅事畀到外國人咩觀感好重要。<br />\n外國係冇義務幫香港，只係利益一致同埋有好嘅正當理由。<br />\n<br />\n其實呢個問題同樣可以spin 到勿只因政見不合就搞鳩人，針對返個政權警隊等<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母死黑警</span></span><br />\n完"},{"pid":"40e1057e02312a40f9c7c4969a2bb5137429ee17","tid":1614411,"uid":157064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:50:56.000Z","msg":"半夜推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b00767442caa1d5ca56ab0c2e19eb532637c657","tid":1614411,"uid":86442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:52:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32e9c2475b9b06f7e95f6c9cc80aa0c32f8c0a35","tid":1614411,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:53:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3d570b4ba6784a717b1a67c5fe174fda16cf862","tid":1614411,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:54:13.000Z","msg":"同摩西分紅海同一道理"},{"pid":"e8d220b7a65a961fd2d4a3820a13de18d3569d27","tid":1614411,"uid":291619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:54:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c19223f1935b98b4b575ee6fd748d7d9dae13dc1","tid":1614411,"uid":60487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8d220b7a65a961fd2